            %div{:id => 'volvo'}
            %div{:id => 'benz'}

        %div{:class => 'row'}
          %span{:class => 'mobile col s12'} 0409 602 968

        %div{:class => 'row'}
          %section{:class => 'about col s6'}
            %h2 About Us
            %p Located in Western Sydney, K & C Auto Electrics is a well established business with over 25 years of experience. We currently service and are trusted by some of New South Wales major transport companies (such as?). Our workshop and mobile units are fully equipped with tools of the highest technology. We have the latest scanning tools on the market today to get your vehicle back on the road fast and keep your business running smoothly. 
